Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SECRET WAY OF PURIFICATION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master's too weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?! All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he joins us for this final battle,\Nhe'll only die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! How can you say that\Nafter Master came to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer this,\Nis Aban's power enough to fight Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This man lost to the old Hadorra once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't stand a chance\Nagainst Hadorra as a Superior Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that our fight has reached this level,\Nwhat use would someone that weak be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all grown in strength\Nthrough battles with powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a wide gap between\Nour current combat power and Aban's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hadorra look like\Nsomeone you could beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Hero, Dai,\Nfought him alone and beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How much stronger\Ndo you think Dai is compared to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of pure combat power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that I'm even\Nhalf as strong as Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your analysis is accurate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as expected of the former Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you being so stuck-up about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to cry to\NMaster Aban more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about a power difference?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master came all this way to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that show of kindness enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness doesn't win battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely stated the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As it stands, Aban is weaker\Nthan Dai or me or even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I won't stand for\Na man this weak to be our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you all want to follow Aban forward,\Nthen I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, I know it's difficult for you\Nto open up to Master Aban...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget him, Maam. Let him whine.\NWho throws a tantrum at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, everything\Nyou have said is true. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let us move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... But Master...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to respect Hyunckel's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is what he wants,\Nthere's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, I know Hyunckel will follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is taking so long?\NReturn to me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there an issue, Sire?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected turn of events.\NAban has returned from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban? Aban, the Hero?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I doubt he possesses\Nthe strength to be any threat to you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The threat is not from his strength.\NDai is far stronger than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But Aban possesses\Nsomething beyond mere strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I originally ordered Hadorra\Nto slay him at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense a strength from him\Ndifferent than the kind I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Left alive, the Disciples of Aban\Nwill grow in power at an alarming rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What of Kill? Where is Kilban?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,While you both bear my name,\Nhe is not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,His purpose is entirely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is not his job to protect me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He exists to kill. That is all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban is quite smart,\Nbut he made a mistake.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He merely wounded his enemy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such a meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our favorite mask, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Left to his own devices,\NI'm sure Kilban will hunt down Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stop Dai and the others,\Nwho've gained momentum from Aban's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My King!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still watching him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't believe Hyunckel\Nwould selfishly say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we approach that entrance, Hyunckel\Nwill be attacked by numerous enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so thick, Popp!\NDon't you understand his intent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly what you did once before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the battle with the Dragon Masters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. I wanted everyone\Nto be able to fight and not worry,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I pretended to be selfish and ran off!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to understand, Popp,\Nwhat he really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel was able to realize\Nwhat my real power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that my power would be\Nessential in navigating Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So he took on\Nthe role of holding off any pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if you all knew the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you would never have let him remain alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, did you realize\NHyunckel's intent from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it at a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel would always trouble me\Nby saying and doing things he didn't mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He would always have that look.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of mix of\Nsadness and remorse in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You won't take\None step beyond here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard! He always does this!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He treats us like children\Nand acts like he knows everything!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He goes and hogs all the glory!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time I see you, I'll kick your butt!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you better not die, Hyunckel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You better survive this!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, monsters of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not your only problem!\NNo enemy can invade the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, I'm going to take care of\Nall of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And secondly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no obstacle can stop\Nthe others who went ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear him apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Hyunckel be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He trained under me because he thought\NI killed his father and wanted revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he actually\Npaid attention to his lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel is following the rules I laid out\Nfor entering enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When charging an enemy fortress,\Nwhat's most vital,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is not taking down enemies in the way,\Nbut preventing being flanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When weakened, the most dangerous thing is\Ngetting attacked from both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when choosing a formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you need powerful members\Nin both the front and the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took that role earlier\Nand managed to hold off that reaper.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You fought Kilban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that Hyunckel noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he took on that role himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when you caught up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I used a spell to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a new spell I've attained called Lilirura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilirura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a type of Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spell to regroup with allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mystic spell that's normally used\Nto regroup when lost in a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master Aban, are you saying\Nyou've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A gate. It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,GRAND CROSS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEGIRAMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAT-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like the Dark Citadel Gate\Nat the entrance of Ban Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you worked\Nwith your dad to destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be even more powerful\Nthan that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!\NTo come all this way only to be blocked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you why\NHyunckel gave me the lead
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,while he stayed back to guard the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The new power I've obtained\Nthrough my training up to this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I've been training\Nthis whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the legendary Carl Kingdom...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,deep in the Cave of Trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the Cave of Trials...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...w-where Leona attained\Nher Minakator spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban must have\Ngone beyond where we went,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,down to far deeper levels\Nin the Cave of Trials!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To attain even more powerful\NPurifying Spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, on the day I lost to Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,while the Amulet of Carl\Ndid save my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my body was badly damaged\Nby my Megante spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sent flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I awoke, I was in the ocean\Nnear Dermline Island.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I realized I had been saved\Nby the Amulet of Carl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there\Nwhen you two began your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dragged my wounded body there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would have been easy to call out\Nand join you on your journey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I couldn't bring myself to.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to help you two\Nto continue to grow...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I couldn't forgive my own weakness.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew that Dai's latent strength\Nalready far exceeded my own.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That meant that even if I went with you,\NI would only hinder your progress.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to train myself in body and soul\Nand gain new abilities of my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or I would not be worthy\Nto fight beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I decided to perfect\Nmy purification magic{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the legendary Cave of Trials.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew that would be\Nthe best possible way to train.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I was lacking in strength, I knew\Nit would help against Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. That explains it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master never really\Nabandoned us after all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been desperately fighting on his own.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the next few months,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I continued down the Cave of Trials\Nfor the ultimate Purifying Spellcraft.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the 50th level,\Nthere were no more spells,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the labyrinth became more complex.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was running low\Non healing items and rations
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and numerous terrifying traps awaited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can discuss my adventures\Nanother time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, at the lower levels,\Nthe cave tests the challenger's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When Princess Leona used Minakator\Non one of the upper levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the final battle was approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What level were you on then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We were 25 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I believe it was\Nsomewhere around 150 levels down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For a human, that must be a new record!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is Master Aban's Purifying Magic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was right! Aban attained\Nthe power of purification!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine a more powerful\NPurifying Spell than Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there must be one.\NHe went down 150 whole levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's six times deeper than 25,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so it must be six times stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get the answer\Nfrom simple math, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a spell more powerful\Nthan Minakator at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But we might find one deeper down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I never found one where I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then what is that spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a spell, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the Secret Way of Haja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret Way of Haja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look.\NIt can prove quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So that's it!\NThe Secret Way of Haja!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a spell, but a secret way\Nto amplify a spell's purifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Used with this Secret Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the evil-nullifying effects of various\Nspells can be amplified to their limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when I rescued Popp, I used the\Nbarrier-nullifying spell Baria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and amplified it using\Nthis Secret Way of Haja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He did that with just\Na Toramama spell?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And obviously, the spell\NI'm about to cast against this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the spell for opening doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Abagamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark portal closed since ancient times...\NI command you to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same as last time!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The door to King Ban's palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, my Master Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I told you before,\Nno one can stop their advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:17.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:28.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:23:02.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:09.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:15.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:20.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:27.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban's Secret Way of Purification\Nopened the gate.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Hyunckel holds off the horde of\Nmonsters, the others enter the palace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually Aban makes a request to Leona.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in Loroi Valley, Crocodine\Nand the others push Zaboera back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Steady Advance of Justice"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
